{"tid":844332,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"法式牛扒屋 La Vache","createTime":"2018-10-01T19:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T04:06:55.000Z","uid":175988,"like":6,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"97ff8134ccd18a4f9179ee1847cbda8493b07f8a","tid":844332,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T19:38:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>La Vache @ 尖咀</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AKDxQi8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAKDxQi8.jpg&h=9b4f7a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>牛扒薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牛扒嫩滑多汁，牛味香濃，食材高質<br />\n<br />\n炭火夠，烤紋靚，牛扒外層食落甘香焦脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幼薯條調味恰當，夠熱夠脆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牛扒生熟度拿捏唔好，一塊medium過熟，另一塊medium rare就偏生，切完搞到成盤都係血水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛扒偏向多根，有啲位幾難咬吓，甚至少少起渣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論:貪新鮮可以一試，想鋸扒去番傳統美國扒房穩陣啲</strong>"},{"pid":"5509ad2b0c88c717ff74a2b656fec25cf000f983","tid":844332,"uid":46576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T19:47:49.000Z","msg":"how much"},{"pid":"87338fbfaf0750c805a10ea81ef1f49cb4bee8c7","tid":844332,"uid":175988,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"5509ad2b0c88c717ff74a2b656fec25cf000f983","tid":844332,"uid":46576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T19:47:49.000Z","msg":"how much"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:20:15.000Z","msg":"午市優惠價$198包合桃沙律+牛扒+無限薯條+泡芙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456e3783e627b4c5243d50b7442276151890df59","tid":844332,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:40:36.000Z",